# PAS version commit workflow

For any PAS Android app (PAS_1, PAS_2, PAS_3, PAS_4) in this family, **never** commit version bumps by calling `git_commit.ps1` or raw `git commit` directly.

Always use the project script from the **PAS project root**:

```bat
app\run_version_update.bat
```

Non-interactive (agent/terminal, auto-dismiss `pause`):

```bat
cmd /c "echo.| app\run_version_update.bat"
```

Run separately per PAS repo (PAS_1, PAS_2, PAS_3, PAS_4). The script bumps version, updates strings, commits, tags, and pushes.
